=== Overview

loop-mount is used to mount the system image and should be true when selinux is enforcing.

==== Options

--- true
this option is used to mount system partition

       --- parameters

       --- code dir

--- false
this option is used to disable support of loop-mount in build

      --- parameters

      --- code dir

--- default
when not explicitly selected in mixin spec file, the default option will be used.
